title: Flight Simulator 2020 - How to - Working Title CJ4 "Hidden" features
description:
In this how to we are going to look at some "hidden" features of the Working Title CJ4 including:

- audio prompts for passengers
- build-in checklist
- custom options to change the display

Working Title CJ4 can be downloaded from this site: https://github.com/Working-Title-MSFS-Mods/fspackages
